<section id="landing-page-section">
  <!-- background image for landing page -->
  <%= image_tag ('having-cows-jumbotron.jpg'), id: 'landing-img' %>
</section>

<section id="biography-section">
  <div id="parallax-biography" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>BIOGRAPHY</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container">
  <div class="biography-text">
    <p>The band has been together <strong>since 2013</strong> consisting of 3 members playing, 1 acoustic and 1 electric guitar and a kick-ass drum beat. At the end of 2013 they decided to evolve their own creativity by starting to write their own music and gigging all around Bloemfontein as they are <strong>a proud Bloem local based act</strong>.</p><p>As recent as June 2014 they released a studio recorded EP named <strong>‘ABIUA’</strong> and from there on promoted towards the project while finding themselves the number one alternative act in Bloemfontein on <strong>Reverbnation</strong>. ‘Die Mystic Boer’ has also announced Having Cows the number one ‘up and coming’ band for 2014 by <strong>winning the Crooked Boer Sessions</strong> in August 2014 and received a partial recording contract to share a compilation CD with fellow great Bloem bands.</p><p>Since November 2015 the band has evolved into the four piece line-up that they find themselves in currently, moving more towards the ‘plugged-in’ vibe doing full band shows. Classified as an <strong>indie band with a twitch of breaking the rules</strong> here and there, the guys from Having Cows play gigs all over South Africa. Proudly opening for local S.A. favourites like <strong>'aKING', ‘Monark’, ‘Moses&nbsp;Metro Man’, ‘Elvis Blue’ and ‘Shortstraw’</strong> in between gigging numerous shows in the city of roses as they stand well known for locally.</p><p>The band has enjoyed some radio play on Tuks FM with the single ‘A Beat In Us All’ off the ABIUA EP in early 2015 and entered the <strong>Tuks FM top 30</strong> charts while sticking around there for 12 weeks on-going peaking at <strong>number 11</strong>. Released on February 2016, they released ‘Tryna Be Lawful’ as a single track which has also been kindly received by <strong>Tuks FM, Kovsie FM and PUK FM</strong> and can be found on these radio stations’ rotational playlists.</p><p>Taking the bigger step towards recording at a more well-known production studio, they worked with <strong>Greg Carlin (Zebra & Giraffe)</strong> at OpenRoom Production studios with Greg producing their single ‘So Much To Gain’. The song was released in late April 2017 through MiniBeast Records as the official distributors.</p><p>Be sure to find the band on any social media platforms and gigging around wherever they are.</p>
  </div> <!-- end biography text -->

  <div class="meet-the-band">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="card">
          <%= image_tag ('ralf-swart.jpg'), class: 'card-img-top img-fluid' %>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Ralf Swart</h5>
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Singing the Songs</h6>
            <p class="card-text">Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf Ralf.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="card">
          <%= image_tag ('gavin-coetser.jpg'), class: 'card-img-top img-fluid' %>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Gavin Coetser</h5>
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Slappin' The Bass</h6>
            <p class="card-text">Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin Gavin.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
        <div class="card">
          <%= image_tag ('koos-le-roux.jpg'), class: 'card-img-top img-fluid' %>
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Koos le Roux</h5>
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Beating the Drums</h6>
            <p class="card-text">Koos Koos Koos Koos Koos Koos Koos Koos Koos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> <!-- end row -->
  </div> <!-- end meet the band -->
</div> <!-- end container -->
</section> <!-- end biography section -->

<section id="discography-section">
  <div id="parallax-discography" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>DISCOGRAPHY</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container img-grid-container">
    <div class="row">
      <% @featured_songs.each do |song| %>
      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4 img-grid">
        <%= link_to image_tag(song.image, class: 'img-fluid'), song %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div> <!-- end row -->
  </div> <!-- end container img-grid-container-->
</section> <!-- end discography section -->

<section>
  <div id="parallax-videos" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>VIDEOS</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container img-grid-container">
    <div class="row">
      <% @featured_videos.each do |video| %>
      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-4 col-lg-4 img-grid">
        <%= link_to image_tag(video.image, class: 'img-fluid'), video %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div> <!-- end row -->
  </div> <!-- end container img-grid-container-->
</section> <!-- end videos section -->

<section id="events-section">
  <div id="parallax-events" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>EVENTS</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table class="table table-hover">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Event</th>
            <th>Venue</th>
            <th>Date</th>
            <th>Entrance</th>
            <th>Tickets Available At:</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% @featured_events.each do |event| %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= event.event_name %></td>
            <td><%= event.venue %></td>
            <td><%= event.date %></td>
            <td>R<%= event.entrance %></td>
            <td><%= event.tickets_available_at %></td>
          </tr>
          <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div> <!-- end table responsive -->
    <br>
    <div class="text-center">
      <%= link_to ('DOWNLOAD OUR EPK'), class: 'btn btn-info' %>
      <span>&amp;</span>
      <%= link_to ('CONTACT US FOR BOOKINGS'), class: 'btn btn-info' %>
    </div>
  </div> <!-- end container -->
</section> <!-- end events section -->
<br>

<section>
  <div id="parallax-merch" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>MERCH</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="carousel slide" id="discography-carousel" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="4000" data-pause="false">
    <div class="carousel-inner">

      <!-- CAROUSEL INDICATORS -->
      <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <% @featured_merchandises.each_with_index do |merchandise, i| %>
        <li data-target="discography-carousel" data-slide-to="<%= i %>"" class="<%= "active" if i == 0 %>">
        </li>
        <% end %>
      </ol>

      <!-- WRAPPER FOR SLIDES -->
      <% @featured_merchandises.each do |merchandise| %>
      <div class="carousel-item <%= "active" if merchandise == @featured_merchandises.first %>">
        <%= image_tag (merchandise.image_url), class: 'd-block img-fluid', alt: 'carousel' %>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <!-- CAROUSEL CONTROLS -->
    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#discography-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#discography-carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div> <!-- end carousel -->
</section> <!-- end merchandise section -->

<section id="contact-section">
  <div id="parallax-contact" class="parallax">
    <!-- background for the paralax effect -->
    <div class="parallax-header text-center">
      <h1>CONTACT US</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-form">
      <%= flash[:notice] %>
      <%= form_tag("/simple_pages/thank_you") do |form| %>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= label_tag :name, "Name", class: "sr-only" %>
        <%= text_field_tag :name, nil, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Name" %>
      </div> <!-- end form-group -->
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= label_tag :email, "Email Address", class: "sr-only" %>
        <%= text_field_tag :email, nil, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Email Address" %>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <%= label_tag :message, "Message", class: "sr-only" %>
        <%= text_area_tag :message, nil, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Give us your thoughts..." %>
      </div>
      <%= submit_tag "Send", class: "btn" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>